<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>344</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<lyrics>[V1]
 qiān lǐ zhī wài de xiǎo cūn zhuāng, shì wǒ men chū fā de de fāng,
 jiǔ yuè de jì jié shì qiū fēng liáng wǒ men bēn pǎo zài hé chǎng.
 rén men dōu zhēng xiān qù shōu gē zhuāng jià wǒ men kuài bǎ hé kǔn bèi huí liáng cāng,
 zǒu guò píng yuán, zǒu guò shān gǎng, zhǔ bì jiā gěi nǐ lì liàng.
 wú xīn qù sī niàn gù xiāng de jǐng shuǐ, yòu tián yòu liáng yòu qīng yòu shuǎng,
 qiān wàn rén de líng hún kě shì bù néng fàng, yī shēng gān yuàn zài wài liú làng.</lyrics>
<title>qiān lǐ zhī wài de xiǎo cūn zhuāng 迦南344</title>
</song>